# Frontend dev – port 5173 only

- The frontend dev server is configured to run on **port 5173** (see `src/frontend/vite.config.js`).
- After applying any frontend change, tell the user: **"Refresh http://localhost:5173 (or hard refresh Cmd+Shift+R) to see changes."**
- Do not suggest or use other ports (5174, 5175, etc.) unless 5173 is in use or the user asks.
